videos.description: Mike Edwards catches a tipped pass and returns it 66 yards for a touchdown to take an early lead over Middle Tennessee.
videos.headline: UK scores on pick-six on first possession of the game

videos.description: Benny Snell Jr. runs untouched for a 7-yard touchdown to give Kentucky a 14-0 lead.
videos.headline: Snell Jr. runs untouched for 7-yard TD

videos.description: Brent Stockstill finds Chaton Mobley in the flat for a 6-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Middle Tennessee's Mobley hauls in 6-yard TD

videos.description: Terry Wilson escapes pressure and fires a strike to TE C.J. Conrad for a 11-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Wilson eludes pressure to fire TD

videos.description: Kentucky's Josh Paschal, who was diagnosed with a malignant melanoma on the bottom of his foot, returns to the field and makes a tackle on third down.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kentucky’s Pashcal returns from cancer to make tackle) 2018/11/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kentucky's Paschal returns from cancer to make tackle

videos.description: Benny Snell Jr. follows his blocks and runs for a 6-yard touchdown to extend Kentucky's lead to 31-10 over Middle Tennessee.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Snell finds a hole for a 6-yard TD

videos.description: Brent Stockstill rockets a back-shoulder pass to Ty Lee for a 10-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Middle Tennessee flings back-shoulder fade for 10-yard TD

videos.description: Brent Stockstill swings a pass to Patrick Smith for a 5-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Middle Tennessee's Smith grabs swing pass for 5-yard TD
